## 0. Project Goal

You will be able to:

* Control the system entirely via the terminal.
* Write modular Bash scripts (POSIX-sh where possible).
* Manage versions using Git (branches, rebase, merge, tags, hooks).
* Make your environment reproducible (simple Dockerfile or Vagrantfile).
* Perform self-research using `man`, `--help`, and official docs instead of asking directly.

